:: Judgment {"position":"2500,500","size":"100,100"}
You stay where you are.

No one is looking at you. No one is asking you anything. The decision has already been made, with or without you.

It would be easy to leave it there.

Samael, taken away. An explanation that fits well enough.

You turn it over anyway.

What you saw. What you heard. What didn't quite line up.

You could accept it.

Or not.
