<span class="highlight">Not Samael.</span>

It holds longer than anything else you've had.

You don't say it. There's no one to say it to that would hear it the same way.

The moment passes like everything else has.

[[You let it go->End-Insight]]
]

(if: not ($saw_A_influence_B and $clues_found >= 5))[
