You woke up still tired. Lottery night always ran late. The five of you crowded around someone's laptop, checking one line each against the numbers. The same Tuesday ritual that had never once paid out in three years.
}
{(live: 2.5s)[
(stop:)
Last night, it did.
]}

{(live: 5s)[
(stop:)
<span class="highlight">This morning, one of you is dead.</span><br><br>
[[The office->Morning]]
